(191, 'Application Orientation for the 2019 SMEA “Grant Program for International Accelerators and Entrepreneurship Development Organizations”', '2019-12-30', 'news', '<p>Application Orientation for the 2019 Small and Medium Enterprise Administration (SMEA), Ministry of Economic Affairs International Startup Campus Demonstration Program“Grant Program for International Accelerators and Entrepreneurship Development Organizations”\r\n	<br>The orientation will cover the following categories: application guide, program reviewing process and budget itemization.\r\n	<br>We look forward to your esteemed presence!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kaohsiung Orientation\r\n	<br>【Date】: January, 6th, 2020\r\n	<br>【Time】: PM 2:00 ~4:00\r\n	<br>【Address】: Computer Skills Foundation&nbsp;/ 7F.-4, No.366, Bo’ai 1st Rd., Sanmin Dist., Kaohsiung City, Taiwan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Taipei Orientation\r\n	<br>【Date】: January, 7th, 2020\r\n	<br>【Time】: PM 2:00 ~4:00\r\n	<br>【Address】:&nbsp;<span data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;k&quot;}\">Startup Terrace /&nbsp;</span>1F, No.496, Sec. 2, Ren’ai Rd., Linkou Dist., New Taipei City 24449, Taiwan</p>\r\n\r\n<p>【Agent】\r\n	<br>14:00-14:30 Registration\r\n	<br>14:30-15:00 Opening / Startup Terrace Overview\r\n	<br>15:00-15:30 Grant Program Overview\r\n	<br>15:30-16:00 Networking / Q&amp;A\r\n	<br>16:00 End\r\n	<br>? Signup Link: <a data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fseminars.tca.org.tw%2FD10o00442.aspx%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ujalLe8PBHakpKD7HQ_n136fHjifz9soJ5e8N-LMc2iQD251CDpJ-p5E%23enroll&amp;h=AT1QHzykTteUK6mwdyc1adxHcyGkDneiheIPdVqP_W6xNrZ9o6E9NaMsC9C8hs0usNmUYDRCF8uOaVEwqkpmR8EiQ-T84TIqP1ByZZU0qhbVVqUHBm61KJDFl1gIYSCEK2_B8J4rOC6xTNvnQTnXlMBbF5ZIYExyt99NKdoUin4UX5n1yT8PAeTS6oU6OJzrAxHADcMI2aVDPV_tZHmSSbi7qdVcj9xoI_FqZ-3SSnmcAk6MN_OWjdin5faEvmT7YNv9WOAyRDUDNZ0jodmdZUBB_gJOhNMfVvHTfnwLKf_W9KIH6dUTw7A6hylJKKpkoPXPK7eZ5cf5MbltV-9OW8YCJqp4VV9EW07QcMQ-LXZBI6pbAKgaOzIgPVquCWJ2-AdMmQlsUtuCmY1H7vfwkNbu-tXgBeoLqZtzWyZa693TD4bbzXfrt5bu1HsVPZpmYf31ry7HeJrPxlRlVpLXvEMpOyOlNStqqVXG1HaDHWfaWGLqK6U0GNF6NLvZ4QqNw-KY0cL_mkXC34zl0AnzikEhSKJ71ua3Y-KsKSGxXF6YQpRc6Jn6eiU749KCqoyXn2HAfFZBK2mdaS5BnksbvrSeS2OpF5bQE3-ZOHCEvM1_NT8wksJ0HpXBnHCoeaAj\" href=\"https://seminars.tca.org.tw/D10o00442.aspx?fbclid=IwAR2ujalLe8PBHakpKD7HQ_n136fHjifz9soJ5e8N-LMc2iQD251CDpJ-p5E#enroll\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://seminars.tca.org.tw/D10o00442.aspx#enroll</a>\r\n	<br>? For more information please call (02)2369-2358</p>', NULL, 1, '2020-01-06 08:54:26', '2020-01-08 03:16:28', NULL),
(192, 'Apply now for Fit 4 Start #10t', '2020-01-03', 'news', '<p>Fit 4 Start in an accelerator programme initiated by the Luxembourg Ministry of the Economy, managed by the Luxinnovation and supported by Technoport and the Luxembourg City Incubator. The programme has already welcomed 78 start-ups from Luxembourg and aboard since its launch in 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Successful applicants could take advantage of：\r\n	<br>?COACHING：16 weeks of experts coaching\r\n	<br>? FUNDING：Grants up to €150,000\r\n	<br>?OFFICE：Free access to co-working space\r\n	<br>?NETWORK：Valuable networking and financing opportunities in Luxembourg’s dynamic start-up ecosystem</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility：\r\n	<br>★ Have an innovation-oriented project and active in the sector(s) referenced in the Fit 4 Start call.\r\n	<br>★ If the Applicant already incorporated a company, this should be not older than 5 years before the time of their Programme application.\r\n	<br>★ Be a team of at least 2 people, at least one of whom will work full time on the project when participating in Fit 4 Start.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?Website: <a data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fit4start.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0UvX42zfQ0AugVmWefcfgKERuT4QBWKE3rzs4GVuo-o0xKa8GJpeENHDU&amp;h=AT2scREO5yqOdkyMBAbG9ftVkSnN5Sbyw36HozDZrwwuf540fRyngcNLd6a4hRQno4WYm90i8HrEEjEezSGXUK56vH1FL2SBm3hylA5xa7b-RTYFIto9hjfDzanZuu9UHgj5lPbspPOLPyBH4PyZBmO937v4Q20T2cNYvB1NcJY0ozjR3b0FTgRKgDJNloSgF_v7ezB5gcHydN0Lroe5M3008s_i8CGIxmgiTSdjnpRfSsNFE1m_tLkEQPP-fSOTOseUSe8XkbksnimssPYC_HlV5Kb5l0BtvsxYM2_e1zPolgC7nyRF_aRyOxtmQpMxGvrZEMqu7VzZ6Zd3IcVhb6vJ0i7RQk6_UjQpvoYbkcs__KqUe_Gq3Vio19-Sz_rkUUdn21n4zD0bwGD_busAVj04_iRcd7ScGg6JRacUcJYhTdSeAQx_fnC32MUeen1ZI4uoVgBCGRf2pUiIA3MDDw4xRVrwlrc9ygt9peasPEM6azSv7rgphi39LrHnapKtafr5VLMqONtJ_MWg6v1Xur58g7ABtRMCmccKpZEpIDYC4xPjxsjQDmJMmKE35iohmwiIi2lNtYFwTqOaM8ukPaFFgCKKVZZ-RXpByLJ-45sK35Fpy4FpmklQZSgS2ERcS4YumUs\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferr