(320, 'Startup Weekend Taipei : The New Normal', '2020-09-08', '', '<h4><strong>Event Theme:The New Normal</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Since the pandemic hit, 2020 has panned out in a way that nobody had expected or could predict. This pandemic will forever change the way we live, play, and work in the next decade. While our generation might not yet be ready to live with these changes, it gives us an opportunity to reimagine our future, “The New Normal”.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the weekend of 11th-13th September, we’re inviting innovators, developers, designers, inventors, and anyone with a passion to help us move on from this crisis, to join us again for a 54 hour weekend to hack ideas that will shape the next decade. Participants will work together and tackle the challenges resulting from the pandemic, and develop prototypes that can help re-imagine the post-pandemic future for Taiwanese citizens and our neighbors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>What Is Techstars Startup Weekend ?</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>In just 54 hours, you will experience the highs, lows, fun, and pressure that make up life at a startup. As you learn how to create a real company, you\'ll meet the very best mentors, investors, cofounders, and sponsors who are ready to help you get started.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Surrounded by smart, passionate people and with the best tools and approaches at your disposal, you’ll take giant leaps toward creating a business, becoming a founder, and connecting with the right people and resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>&nbsp;Information</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>(1) Ticketing: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020\">https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020</a>\r\n	<br>(2) FB Event Page: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020-fb\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020-fb\">https://bit.ly/swtaipei2020-fb</a>\r\n	<br>(3) FB Fanpage: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SW.Taipei/\">https://www.facebook.com/SW.Taipei/</a>\r\n	<br>(4) Techstars Official Page: TBD\r\n	<br>(5) Venue Location: <a href=\"https://g.page/TerminalC?share\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://g.page/TerminalC?share\">https://g.page/TerminalC?share</a></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Date: &nbsp;2020/09/11 - 09/13</li>\r\n	<li>Time:\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Friday 18:00 - 22:00</li>\r\n			<li>Saturday 9:00 - 22:00</li>\r\n			<li>Sunday 9:00 - 20:00</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Venue:\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>No.92, Sec. 3, Jianguo N. Rd., Zhongshan Dist., Taipei City 10482, Taiwan&nbsp;</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, '2020-09-07 09:42:33', '2020-09-07 09:42:59', NULL),
(321, 'The first step of starting a business in Taiwan - How to build up your dream team?', '2020-09-08', 'startups, event, Taiwan, talents', '<p><strong>Description:</strong>\r\n	<br>The increased interest in globalization and the changes in Taiwanese policies for foreign startups have prompted more and more foreigners to choose Taiwan as a location to start their business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first thing these foreigners encountered was not to set up a company in Taiwan, but to recruit suitable people to join their team. So you may have some questions. What type of talents should I recruit? What questions should I ask when recruiting talents?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any of the above questions, then don’t miss the event held at InnoSqaure. 【Global Partner Deputy Director of STARTBOARD】- Mason Lin will share and analyze with you to build up your dream team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Organizers:</strong>\r\n	<br>(1) Economic Development Department, New Taipei City Government\r\n	<br>(2) STARTBOARD</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Time:&nbsp;</strong>\r\n	<br>2020, September 18th (FRI), 2-5 PM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Venue:&nbsp;</strong>\r\n	<br>InnoSquare (3F., No. 108, Sec. 1, Chongxin Rd., Sanchong Dist., New Taipei City 241, Taiwan (R.O.C.))</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Speaker:</strong>\r\n	<br>【Global Partner Deputy Director of STARTBOARD】- Mason Lin</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Agenda:</strong>\r\n	<br>1:30 PM- 2:00 PM Registration\r\n	<br>2:00 PM- 2:10 PM Opening Remark\r\n	<br>2:10 PM- 4:00 PM Topic: The first step of starting a business in Taiwan, how to build up your dream team?\r\n	<br>4:00 PM- 4:30 PM Q&amp;A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(This event will proceed in English)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Apply here:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://forms.gle/kKMp75ctRL2vnZZDA\">forms.gle/kKMp75ctRL2vnZZDA</a></p>', NULL, 1, '2020-09-08 03:36:42', '2020-09-08 08:55:26', NULL),
(322, 'How to hire foreigners in Taiwan?', '2020-09-08', 'foreigners, Taiwan, worker, hire, process', '<div dir=\"auto\">As Taiwan gradually recognizes the importance of <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/globalization?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZWurdg_Xpg7_t5CVhHQK-w72MlR08OoA8s4JofNcTwddNqtNCaCCAVAWsIFsGlIrc_PmejV8JmI02D3ACGPZ7x9UW7INIXo4u9iQOofLFe2cjN-OUIW4kvpslrS6W3_ZJLVSixoacA_XQm0upbrismQ74AFhtGWs68AqJESTTwgQpvNvsqfuzddpmm7NB03Dlg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#globalization</a>, many companies are actively expanding abroad and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/hiring?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZWurdg_Xpg7_t5CVhHQK-w72MlR08OoA8s4JofNcTwddNqtNCaCCAVAWsIFsGlIrc_PmejV8JmI02D3ACGPZ7x9UW7INIXo4u9iQOofLFe2cjN-OUIW4kvpslrS6W3_ZJLVSixoacA_XQm0upbrismQ74AFhtGWs68AqJESTTwgQpvNvsqfuzddpmm7NB03Dlg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#hiring</a> foreign employees.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">This video summarizes the important guidelines to common questions that Taiwanese employers or foreign employees have:\r\n	<br><strong><br></strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>Taiwanese <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/employer?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZWurdg_Xpg7_t5CVhHQK-w72MlR08OoA8s4JofNcTwddNqtNCaCCAVAWsIFsGlIrc_PmejV8JmI02D3ACGPZ7x9UW7INIXo4u9iQOofLFe2cjN-OUIW4kvpslrS6W3_ZJLVSixoacA_XQm0upbrismQ74AFhtGWs68AqJESTTwgQpvNvsqfuzddpmm7NB03Dlg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#employer</a>:</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">1. Does my company qualify to hire a foreigner?</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">2. Is there a minimum salary?\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>Foreign <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/employee?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZWurdg_Xpg7_t5CVhHQK-w72MlR08OoA8s4JofNcTwddNqtNCaCCAVAWsIFsGlIrc_PmejV8JmI02D3ACGPZ7x9UW7INIXo4u9iQOofLFe2cjN-OUIW4kvpslrS6W3_ZJLVSixoacA_XQm0upbrismQ74AFhtGWs68AqJESTTwgQpvNvsqfuzddpmm7NB03Dlg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#employee</a>:</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">1. What are the requirements to become an employee in Taiwan?</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">2. How long can I stay?</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"fr-video fr-dvb fr-draggable\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"true\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tRKBgt6kA5A\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">If you have any questions regarding the hiring process please contact us directly! &nbsp;\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">STARTBOARD email: contact@startboard.co</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>Follow our youtube channel:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://reurl.cc/WLrv7Z?fbclid=IwAR25yaz60eAjUQAtsisP_DOzcnzx-x31xwjzTjYZsvOmPae5OAzDejSaf-s\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>https://reurl.cc/WLrv7Z</strong></a></div>', NULL, 1, '2020-09-08 03:40:30', '2020-09-08 03:40:30', NULL),
(323, 'Entrepreneur\'s Series Course -The Opportunities in Southeast Asia', '2020-09-11', '', '<p>Are you still evaluating the Southeast Asian market?Starting from Taiwan looking at greater Southeast Asia, and actively participating in the formation of this vast market.Let\'s develop the most suitable opportunities and sales strategies for Taiwanese companies with digital transformation‼</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Expert in international relations and industry trends.Dr. Alan H.Yang, Executive Director of Executive Director of Taiwan-Asia Exchange Foundation (TAEF) who will bring insightful industry analysis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>⏰Time: September 16th, AM 11:00 ~ PM 12:10</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?Location: Startup Terrace (Rm. 1801B, 18F., No. 502, Sec. 2, Ren’ai Rd., Linkou Dist., New Taipei City 244, Taiwan (R.O.C.))</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?RSVP :&nbsp;<a data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2Fv9yl2%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Zuc6DXJRQJGTNqcqbL1TvDdo7N_7OKzv8EWSXrfP_XvxTTy5qbBauI2E&amp;h=AT1j00QwfcCzhLfdFl2JCjRbpL-r4A5EHSOW4KHZ2NyU96BmODT0yh8Z_XeCBu5OxgBKwK0-xBrDRFAktJkr8ixjkJ0on6DN22BKrdwvmNPlN4KFnGJ-xwx-2YrHFKW80arbbIHkAL1am46qGDkb51LYnvvTeLMVCFhOcFrwi1VigZtZoSweoIa5nXcW_uPrRiC-wwk_s76Fo2Z20nX6U75G0Nr92KQt_hMMoh9n8qc2aoaqRuZdguR6_UsHIKENHfMmhpl0Pfr-jSMrZvY1s_izQ66IbNCHIvGj5EfcrQHdpyaLgxXJND-jaZVBQLwOMd2fzK0mAj0kRWK7nSJZNq_5fM6Wc_yubwBanJguC_j9agp4dKjaFFxdmvBPjoTc1_lBGrqLNZYafnPyKKluKOL-NPqg3xs6kP82ZltNhd-B_KcV-wkr58T6qXrN-1QsTQZts4nX5kwf0yytxsrJ8lQ49Ouwu0Nfo_KJCOBxV8rozTUSGyIsp83QTstO3xgBs7wovBevTYt0lpjYy3c4XIxYdV9_20U63YB1xIasaq_eHd9hn5Nsd9pl9ErfZrzQM9RT7YQvLRq-WGRFmmPJ0mW_oCwIftxLOz0WTw7E1kxLzBwfK0yMYtmAmqQBqdiL\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/v9yl2</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>?Click for more info:&nbsp;<a data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2Fv84nm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Zuc6DXJRQJGTNqcqbL1TvDdo7N_7OKzv8EWSX