\n\r\n<p>He shared that IoT Service Hub was built upon the realization that many small quantities and diverse IoT projects are ignored as the focus are mostly on big volume audiences. Therefore, with the aim to provide services and development resources to all projects and teams as well as giving assistance from the first stage, development cycles to launching, the Hub currently provides more than 8 different kinds of A-IoT development kit: EV Board, SOM, developer friendly material and also gathers experts in Taiwan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With no payment needed, the IoT Service Hub accepts application all year around providing series of consultations to matchmaking activities that will help before the official launch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To bring both on-site and online audiences a better understanding of the various aspects that the IoT can be used in, several manufacturers were invited to this event to introduced their business and how the business itself integrates with IoT. There are SINBON Electronics Co., Ltd, OHGA SmartThings Co., Ltd, KO\'LAB Industrial Design &amp; Research Co., Ltd, and VALD Co., Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>IoT Service Hub role in the business’s development</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the sharing of the four manufacturer companies, 2 teams were also invited to share about their successful cases, Ms. Hsi-Lu Chao, as the Associate Professor of National Yang Ming Chiao Tung University sharing about National Yang-Ming University-Vipasyana: A Full-Functional Wireless ECG for Healthcare A-IoT and Business Director of Ocare-Automated Disinfection S', NULL, 0, '2022-08-26 08:49:04', '2022-08-26 08:52:12', '2022-08-26 08:52:12');
INSERT INTO `ip_ieit_news` (`id`, `title`, `art_date`, `tag`, `content`, `pic`, `enabled`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`) VALUES
(508, 'IoT Service Hub Can Help! Turning Ideas into Products!', '2022-08-26', '', '<p>IoT Service Hub is an IoT development base operated under the support of the Industrial Development Bureau of the Ministry of Economic Affairs, providing manufacturing-oriented guidance programs and many other services offered to help companies in developing prototypes, connections from varieties of industry, prepares the products for market launching and many other assistances in terms of soft-and hardware, cloud platform, product design, marketing, and data application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The IoT Service Hub’s International seminar is one of IDB’s many efforts to let the world know more about the platform and help entrepreneurs, IoT services and IoT solutions users to leverage this platform capabilities in realizing their dream and to turn their ideas into products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Source：https://www.ideas-hatch.com/iot_service_hub.jsp</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Established and supported ,100+ project team and 400+ successful cases</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Attended by Mr. Cheng-Chin Lu, the Deputy Director of Information Technology Industries Division, Industrial Development Bureau (IDB), Ministry of Economic Affairs,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>he stated that to keep up with the ICT trends, IDB has already built IoT Service Hub as a platform to foster, build, and enabling environment in supporting entrepreneurs and teams to leverage IoT solution. Furthermore, over these years, they have established more than 100 project teams and supported over 400 successful cases. Their aim in the future is to go beyond Taiwan, to the global stage.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Aims to provide</strong><strong>&nbsp;services and development resources to all projects and teams in IoT industry</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This event was also attended by the Director of Institute for Information Industry (III) and Director of IoT Service Hub, Mr. Calvin Tsai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He shared that IoT Service Hub was built upon the realization that many small quantities and diverse IoT projects are ignored as the focus are mostly on big volume audiences. Therefore, with the aim to provide services and development resources to all projects and teams as well as giving assistance from the first stage, development cycles to launching, the Hub currently provides more than 8 different kinds of A-IoT development kit: EV Board, SOM, developer friendly material and also gathers experts in Taiwan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With no payment needed, the IoT Service Hub accepts application all year around providing series of consultations to matchmaking activities that will help before the official launch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To bring both on-site and online audiences a better understanding of the various aspects that the IoT can be used in, several manufacturers were invited to this event to introduced their business and how the business itself integrates with IoT. There are SINBON Electronics Co., Ltd, OHGA SmartThings Co., Ltd, KO\'LAB Industrial Design &amp; Research Co., Ltd, and VALD Co., Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>IoT Service Hub role in the business’s development</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the sharing of the four manufacturer companies, 2 teams were also invited to share about their successful cases, Ms. Hsi-Lu Chao, as the Associate Professor of National Yang Ming Chiao Tung University sharing about National Yang-Ming University-Vipasyana: A Full-Functional Wireless ECG for Healthcare A-IoT and Business Director of Ocare-Automated Disinfection Solution for Sharing Motor , Mr. David Tai, was also invited to share their stories.Amidst different background and concerns, both have the similarity in proceeding and integrating their products in the IoT industry as well as were supported by the IoT Service Hub.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ms. Hsi-Lu Chao, is very grateful for the support of many instances including Institute for Information Industry (III), that created the IoT Service Hub program in connecting stakeholders and medical centers to make the Vipasyana available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And Mr. David Tai stated that IoT Service Hub has played a big role in the whole process by connecting Ocare with partners such as WeMo &amp; GoShare, also in the introduction of mass production resources, as well as, media exposure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Expanding to the ASEAN and India Market requires taking certain factors into account.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Taiwan, recognized as a country with an incredible ICT ecosystem across the world, with the accessibility to incredible platform and services of the IoT Service Hub to provide development resources, companies who are or interested to expand their business to ASEAN market should consider several factors. With this, CEO of STARTBOARD, Mr. Uniform, was invited to share about ASEAN Market development – International Resource Integration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Uniform explained that there are many process and cost needed to be estimated upon developing business in Taiwan, such as: entrepreneurs visa application, working spaces, networking. In addition, he stressed out that it is important for entrepreneurs to have local network and connection for the best decision-making process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following after the sharing sessions, entrepreneurs, groups, and startups interested or wondering for possibility cooperation in near future in relation with the IoT industry, are all welcomed to contact the IoT service hub.</p>', NULL, 1, '2022-08-26 08:53:56', '2022-08-30 07:55:30', '2022-08-30 07:55:30'),
(509, 'NASA Space Apps Challenge Registraton Open!', '2022-08-27', '', '<p><span dir=\"auto\">On October 1-2, 2022 NASA and a global group of space agency partners are inviting makers, builders, artists, coders, entrepreneurs, designers, and storytellers to participate in the 11th NASA International Space Apps Challenge. By using NASA’s free and open data and the space agency partners’ data, Space Apps teams will solve challenges and work collaboratively to create scientific discoveries that can help improve life on Earth. During a 2-day hackathon event, participants from around the world will create teams and use space-based data to develop solutions to challenges the world is facing on Earth and in space.&nbsp;</span><span dir=\"auto\">Register here:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://2022.spaceappschallenge.org/auth/signup/\">https://2022.spaceappschallenge.org/auth/signup/</a><span dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br><span dir=\"auto\">Connect with the&nbsp;</span><a dir=\"auto\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/hashtag/spaceapps\" spellcheck=\"false\">#SpaceApps</a><span dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;community!&nbsp;</span>\r\n	<br><span dir=\"auto\">Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.spaceappschallenge.org/\">https://www.spaceappschallenge.org/</a></span>\r\n	<br><span dir=\"auto\">Instagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nasa_spaceapps/\">https://www.instagram.com/nasa_spaceapps/</a></span>\r\n	<br><span dir=\"auto\">Twitter:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/spaceapps\">https://twitter.com/spaceapps</a></span>\r\n	<br><span dir=\"auto\">Facebook:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spaceappschallenge\">https://www.facebook.com/spaceappschallenge</a></span></p>', NULL, 1, '2022-08-26 09:39:09', '2022-08-26 09:39:45', NULL),
(510, '9/1 Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market !', '2022-08-26', 'startup', '<h3 dir=\"ltr\">【Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market】</h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Talents cultivation and international marketing is an important asset and issue towards start-up teams. We not only nurture and incubate, but also accompany and accelerate; Furthermore, STARTBOARD and CrossBond have a long history of being involved in the ASEAN and India markets with dedication to provide integrated services ,companionship , mentoring and partnership to new start-up teams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We are pleased to announce that on September 1, 2022, we will expand to Kaohsiung to hold the event「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」focusing on international talents and cross-border marketing, together with STARTBOARD’s international talents network and CrossBond’s marketing insights, who will bring their years of experiences to share in Kaohsiung.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」invites：</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">ASEAN and India Incubator/ STARTBOARD CEO - Uniform Lin</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">International Entrepreneur/ Banana King CEO－ Abraham Raphael</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Cross-border e-commerce brand accelerator/ Rocketindo Founder － Daniel LIu</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Cross-border e-commerce brand accelerator / ISheEra Founder－Antonius Agoeng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」inviting：</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are a new startups team</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who want to grab business opportunities in ASEAN and India</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are preparing to start a business</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are struggling to find excellent talents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Join us as we head South to Kaohsiung, looking ahead towards international！</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Date: 1st September 2022</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Time: 10：30～14：30</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>', NULL, 0, '2022-08-29 16:37:38', '2022-08-30 07:45:51', '2022-08-30 07:45:51'),
(511, '9/1 Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market Event!', '2022-08-26', 'startup', '<h3 dir=\"ltr\">9/1 Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market Event !</h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Talents cultivation and international marketing is an important asset and issue towards start-up teams. We not only nurture and incubate, but also accompany and accelerate; Furthermore, STARTBOARD and CrossBond have a long history of being involved in the ASEAN and India markets with dedication to provide integrated services ,companionship , mentoring and partnership to new start-up teams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We are pleased to announce that on September 1, 2022, we will expand to Kaohsiung to hold the event「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」focusing on international talents and cross-border marketing, together with STARTBOARD’s international talents network and CrossBond’s marketing insights, who will bring their years of experiences to share in Kaohsiung.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」invites：</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">ASEAN and India Incubator/ STARTBOARD CEO - Uniform Lin</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">International Entrepreneur/ Banana King CEO－ Abraham Raphael</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Cross-border e-commerce brand accelerator/ Rocketindo Founder － Daniel LIu</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Cross-border e-commerce brand accelerator / ISheEra Founder－Antonius Agoeng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">「Moving Toward ASEAN and Global Market」inviting：</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are a new startups team</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who want to grab business opportunities in ASEAN and India</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are preparing to start a business</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Those who are struggling to find excellent talents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Join us as we head South to Kaohsiung, looking ahead towards international！</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Date: 1st September 2022</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Time: 10：30～14：30</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Venue: Yawan Startup Terrace 3F , Command Center &nbsp;(3F, No. 25, Chenggong 2nd Rd, Qianzhen District, Kaohsiung City, 806)</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Language: The whole event is conducted in Chinese</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Remarks: Free registration and limited meals are provided</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Registration link：<strong>https://stli.iii.org.tw/news-event.aspx?no=16&amp;d=1165</strong></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, '2022-08-29 16:39:01', '2022-08-29 16:39:01', NULL),
