. Hsi-Lu Chao, as the Associate Professor of National Yang Ming Chiao Tung University sharing about National Yang-Ming University-Vipasyana: A Full-Functional Wireless ECG for Healthcare A-IoT and Business Director of Ocare-Automated Disinfection Solution for Sharing Motor , Mr. David Tai, was also invited to share their stories.Amidst different background and concerns, both have the similarity in proceeding and integrating their products in the IoT industry as well as were supported by the IoT Service Hub.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/en/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1661845832362.jpeg\" style=\"width: 412px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Successful Case sharing by Ms. Hsi-Lu Chao, as the Associate Professor of National Yang Ming Chiao Tung University about National Yang-Ming University-Vipasyana.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ms. Hsi-Lu Chao, is very grateful for the support of many instances including Institute for Information Industry (III), that created the IoT Service Hub program in connecting stakeholders and medical centers to make the Vipasyana available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/en/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1661845863139.jpeg\" style=\"width: 412px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Successful Case sharing by Mr. David Tai, Business Director of Ocare.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>And Mr. David Tai stated that IoT Service Hub has played a big role in the whole process by connecting Ocare with partners such as WeMo &amp; GoShare, also in the introduction of mass production resources, as well as, media exposure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/en/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1661845886410.jpeg\" style=\"width: 418px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ASEAN Market development – International Resource Integration” by Mr.Uniform, CEO of STARTBOARD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Expanding to the ASEAN and India Market requires taking certain factors into account.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Taiwan, recognized as a country with an incredible ICT ecosystem across the world, with the accessibility to incredible platform and services of the IoT Service Hub to provide development resources, companies who are or interested to expand their business to ASEAN market should consider several factors. With this, CEO of STARTBOARD, Mr. Uniform, was invited to share about ASEAN Market development – International Resource Integration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Uniform explained that there are many process and cost needed to be estimated upon developing business in Taiwan, such as: entrepreneurs visa application, working spaces, networking. In addition, he stressed out that it is important for entrepreneurs to have local network and connection for the best decision-making process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following after the sharing sessions, entrepreneurs, groups, and startups interested or wondering for possibility cooperation in near future in relation with the IoT industry, are all welcomed to contact the IoT service hub.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/en/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/1661845911957.jpeg\" style=\"width: 415px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Brief Networking session</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 1, '2022-08-30 07:52:16', '2023-09-25 13:51:30', NULL),
(513, '2022 Meet Greater South comes to an end!', '2022-09-02', '', '<div dir=\"auto\">During the 2022 Meet Greater South exhibition, SMEA specially assembled Stratup Terrace Kaohsiung, Innovative Legal Clinic, international enterprises and 12 startups to jointly exhibit.\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">In addition, the Deputy Minister of MOEA, Mr. Chern-Chyi Chen also joins us on August 27th for the Taiwan-Singapore Startups Pitch Event, to meet our startups working on innovative solutions in different fields.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>The event ended successfully and injected robust and innovative energy into the southern startups ecosystem!</div>', NULL, 1, '2022-09-02 01:52:45', '2022-09-02 01:53:11', NULL),
(514, 'Hack Award 2023 Call for Speakers Now Open!', '2022-09-03', '', '<p>The “Hack Award” is a global business plan contest where entrepreneurs will give a talk and showcase their ideas and business models. In this coming year, we will be focusing mainly on \"Future Society (abundant, secure and sustainable society),\" focusing on the fields of \"CleanTech\", \"FinTech\" and \"SportsTech\". Domestic and international startup will be presenting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Outline of \"Hack Award 2023\"</strong>\r\n	<br>Date: February 21st, 2023 (Tuesday) 3:35 PM – 5:25 PM(JST)(TBC)\r\n	<br>Venue: Knowledge Capital Congress Center (Osaka City)\r\n	<br>*More details will be announced when available.</p>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Theme and Target Fields:</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Future Society (abundant, secure and sustainable society)</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">With a main focus on \"CleanTech\", \"FinTech\" and \"SportsTech\"</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">For more details for application:</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a href=\"https://www.innovation-osaka.jp/hackosaka/en/hack-award.php\">https://www.innovation-osaka.jp/hackosaka/en/hack-award.php</a></div>', NULL, 1, '2022-09-02 02:03:11', '2022-09-02 02:05:26', NULL),
(515, 'U.S. Taiwan High-Tech Forum 2019: Bridging Taiwan with Silicon Valley', '2019-11-19', 'news', '<p>On November 9th, the annual U.S. Taiwan High-Tech Forum (UTHF) took place in Silicon Valley, California at the Hilton hotel in Santa Clara. In its consecutive event for 22 years now, this year’s theme is called&nbsp;<strong>Exploit the Innovation Opportunities Enabled by Intelligent Connectivity: The combination of 5G, AI and Massive IoT</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The event includes a strong line-up of industry expert speakers who spoke within the theme and attendance was full-house throughout the day. The speakers cover topics ranging from global trends in 5G, applications of Artificial Intelligence in 5G core network systems, 5G manufacturing test challenges in millimeter wave (mmWave) and 5G network security.</p>\r\n<div class=\"al-section al-photo \">\r\n	<figure><img class=\"image fr-fic fr-dii\" title=\"UTHF 2019\" src=\"https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2019-11/img-1574067351-44778@900.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2019-11/img-1574067351-44778@900.jpg 400w,https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2019-11/img-1574067351-44778@900.jpg 600w,https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2019-11/img-1574067351-44778@900.jpg 900w\" style=\"width: 800px;\">\r\n		<figcaption>Full capacity with over 200 attendees at UTHF 2019 (www.uthf.org) / Photograph:UTHF 2019</figcaption>\r\n	</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Besides speaker talks and panel discussion, there was also live demo tables on-site with 5G instrument solutions for cellular V2X from Rohde &amp; Schwartz and 5G millimeter wave (mmWave) test solution from TMYTEK, a Taiwan start-up company who has invented an innovative fast-scan and low-effective approach for 5G mmWave production test along with antenna validation and other test functions in R&amp;D lab. 5G mmWave, operating in high frequency, impose a variety of challenges including testability due to huge path loss from beamforming and difficulty in module-based 5G mmWave over-the-air (OTA) testing. TMYTEK’s mmWave experts have come up with a solution that solves this known problem in the wireless industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a high-profile event bridging the cross-border exchange between Silicon Valley and Taiwan high-tech communities, UTHF has become the flagship event for individuals working in large companies, start-ups as wel', NULL, 0, '2022-09-23 14:46:53', '2022-09-23 14:55:54', '2022-09-23 14:55:54'),
(516, '0926test', '2022-09-26', '#startup', '<p>0926test0926test0926test0926test</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"/storage/app/media/uploaded-files/%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97101%E8%A7%80%E6%99%AF%E5%8F%B0%E9%96%80%E7%A5%A8.jpg\" style=\"width: 363px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-result=\"success\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>正常：<a href=\"//www.google.com\">Google</a>\r\n	<br>正常：<a href=\"#\" title=\"https://www.google.com\">Google</a>\r\n	<br>正常：<a href=\"#\" title=\"http://www.google.com\">Google</a>\r\n	<br>正常：<a href=\"#\" title=\"//www.google.com\">Google</a>\r\n	<br>正常：<a href=\"#\">https://www.google.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"//startup.sme.gov.tw/news\">https://startup.sme.gov.tw/news</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"//www.accupass.com/?area=north\">https://www.accupass.com/?area=north</a></p>', NULL, 1, '2022-09-26 02:19:53', '2022-09-26 02:44:41', '2022-09-26 02:44:41'),
