(594, '2023 International SpaceTech Startup Supporting Program held successfully', '2023-10-02', '', '<div dir=\"auto\">pace technology has garnered significant global traction in the recent years. Hence, the Small and Medium Enterprise Administration (SMEA) promoted &nbsp;“International SpaceTech Startup Supporting Program”, and selected 16 outstanding global SpaceTech startups from 7 different countries across diverse space-related fields this year. &nbsp;Their journey in Taiwan from mid-August to mid-September. &nbsp;We hope Taiwan’s Space industry may strengthened through cooperation between foreign start-ups and Taiwanese manufacturers.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">During this one-month period, we, along with the startups, we’re very excited to see our efforts come to fruition. Through over 30 business matchmaking meetings with nearly 50 Taiwanese companies and research institutes, the startups were able to create deep connections with the SpaceTech related supply chain in Taiwan. As testaments of their successful engagements, Memorandum of Understandings (MOUs) were signed between <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/atgenomix?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#ATGENOMIX</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/vellon?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#Vellon</a> Space Private Limited, &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/taicrystal?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#TaiCrystal</a> International Technologies Co., Ltd. and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/hex20?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#HEX20</a>, as well as between <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/aegiverse?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#Aegiverse</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/hex20?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZV-Kmwf3zIN_rrwQj8Lj8vmO4o3raZAGf6VjxJGyUg387I6nd_tpFwNoaEVlmhwb1kFdcvfQ4zQYJnRMFkfjUtnvyRbvNayk7darUtEKSgCn_8b0bnLe-hysZU5fc-eR8PGAPqJV2JrmWzaA9qrh1Gji1zlCCQ4-38jIYU3h7lsTd9OaY54vGTqcgaxubJDL-Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\" tabindex=\"0\">#HEX20</a>. In addition, there are also several ongoing international collaborations in progress.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Let us congratulate our 16 startups for their fruitful journey in Taiwan!</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Astrogate Labs</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Axiom Space</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Delta-V Robotics</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．deltaVision GmbH</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．GalaxEye Space</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Hex20 Pty Ltd</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Hikade Technologies s.r.o.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Inspecity Space Labs Pvt Ltd</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．ONE3D s.r.o.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．SatSure</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．SpaceDrone&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Spacemanic Ltd.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Transcend Satellite Technology LLP</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;．Xovian Aerospace Pvt Ltd</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;%', NULL, 1, '2023-10-05 06:02:20', '2023-10-06 02:25:56', NULL),
