(630, 'Taiwan‘s Startup Terrace Kaohsiung 【2024 Soft-Landing Program 】 Opens for Applications', '2024-04-05', '', '<div dir=\"auto\">Startup Terrace Kaohsiung (STK), proudly supported by the Ministry of Economic Affairs is thrilled to unveil its 2024 Soft-Landing Program.\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Building on our successful track record since 2021, where 450+ startups have been nurtured with business and investor connections facilitated, STK continues its mission to foster innovation and entrepreneurship internationally.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Focus on 5G, AIoT, smart manufacturing, smart harbor, and green-tech development &amp; transformation.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Selected startups can expect the following experiences and benefits:</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Guidance to the Southern Taiwan market</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Real-site visits &amp; business tours</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Targeted matchmaking, linking with VC, accelerators</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Participation in startup events</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Additionally, participants will receive:</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Accommodation Subsidy(Kaohsiung only): USD50 per day (limit &lt; 30 days)</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">1 month free use of co-working space and facilities</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Free participation in the Soft-Landing Program</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">1-on-1 business matchmaking service</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Participation in the 2024 Meet Greater South Expo and Pitch event</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">Certificate upon completion of the Soft-Landing Program, becoming global startup ambassadors of Startup Terrace Kaohsiung</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">For more information, visit: <a href=\"https://www.accupass.com/go/2024softlanding?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR3G6zSFz5W_PRL4uFC00Oiss-1jYBFLptIWpkkBqD58IIbyLT6PJioiRjA_aem_AafA098w_YRT5MDfjh-L23-nFJHZGuEYKNS0qO3Vcmd9s49_gDtrtdjQisaq7MGgpI5eS7HlaMQOX7dLYH6Y_2hK\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.accupass.com/go/2024softlanding</a></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>or contact STK’s representative, Ms. Vanessa Lee, at: vanessalee@vnrc.tw</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>We are looking forward to seeing you in Taiwan!!</div>', NULL, 1, '2024-04-29 06:36:22', '2024-04-29 06:36:22', NULL),
(631, 'The 23rd Business Startup Award is coming!', '2024-04-24', '', '<div dir=\"auto\">This annual national startup awards, known as the \"Golden Horse Award for Startups,\" is now open for registration!</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">It must be a self-developed innovative product, technology, process or service (including technical service, knowledge service, business service), etc., and has been commercialized or mass-produced (used).</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;Free one-on-one business consulting</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;Extensive networking opportunities and market connections</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Participate -&gt; Interact and exchange with large enterprises</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Winning -&gt; More resources/business opportunities come knocking</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Join now: <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstartup.sme.gov.tw%2Fstartupaward%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR03myrhak1P2uoISB3IJwDxIPnhxPmatRiZNkXw7fD6SviXytvoGMdbK5M_aem_AadZBEOFr5lM2_BujgvzmCKQyCa1Br_A7ZSQu0fRCLJrSAqQu80bL6o5aqT5UCAkk_lWgqqFXMwmKsSFpe3AuJT-&amp;h=AT2fqBX3IahFe4EScP465lwViKxGRbuGIgDsje_UaYVj_Fk8ztiNWzpQBxlC5mZXesrl3_xeLxJFMJnGXMzH_y9oqT_FKIZJQWpeVhxU0vyXpRKJYwv278803vy_qMfw-Z64&amp;__tn__=-UK-R&amp;c[0]=AT3m3DQ06qQHbLs69Xsp1rF428U2pp2eoKA9i4U9ZkSIPPwqUtezd5LR5VRdxZX4ai78H6sSLZ-aj1TatZMg-x4vUkEn9kyCUkzl4x9IHr6a6OM-i9ni0rW_MEREsUNe4TN0tOOHZyMTXjz2_v_vo6lIlox2cSi2Oj_WkeWT_1rjfRLyVSAN9l_Li0321PzbZ8QHV9wr6NrdCg3FBznSGNHWEw4xYL0zl4A6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://startup.sme.gov.tw/startupaward/</a></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">For the latest updates, please follow: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BusinessStartupAward?__cft__[0]=AZX3mgMMpQh5FGpo4vW02dGbkBbctblB_j1ctEqf7hQVU1PS8mO1d57OK63i_G8HHzKNTCfIF_VQ0ZUAk1rIZqpxuF6dqFRWuodvN09XCjhvcZCuM9Zw_og4l99BW6lXlAsyF1xjvUiVA2C7CR4gqZQvIjxl98A6AN8PWa-w5p4RgGop2NWjQFej0C5_M73HWGLnUqUWoonyXqCs9ON4qcJK&amp;__tn__=-]K-R\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/BusinessStartupAward</a></div>', NULL, 1, '2024-04-29 06:43:11', '2024-04-29 06:45:48', NULL),
(632, 'Utilizing the \'Moneyball\' Concept to Scout Talented Engineers: GitRoll Aims to Become an \'International Talent Scout\'', '2024-04-18', '', '<blockquote>\r\n\r\n	<p>Stepping into the office with youthful faces, one wouldn’t imagine that this team, with an average age of under 25, is already experienced in entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>Rebranded from the former metaverse startup team Metamory, the GitRoll team officially launched in 2024. Feng Ruei Guo (pictured on the right), the co-founder of GitRoll, remarked, \" Unlike our past experiences, we\'ve learned the importance of targeting the right market needs.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This time, they are targeting the pain point of \"difficulty finding engineers\" and releasing an evaluation system that scans through engineers\' code to assess their coding ability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On one hand, GitRoll assists engineers who possess the ability but are constrained by factors such as their educational background or experience to find a job that matches their abilities. On the other hand, it helps enterprises eliminate unqualified choices and discover undiscovered talent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://image-cdn.learnin.tw/bnextmedia/image/album/2024-03/img-1711612955-85293.jpg?w=1200&amp;output=webp\" alt=\"Gitroll diagram\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 900px;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>GitRoll not only assists engineers with capabilities but hindered by factors such as education and experience to find jobs commensurate with their abilities but also aids enterprises in weeding out unsuitable candidates while seeking out undiscovered talent. / Image Credits: GitRoll官網</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Breaking the Academic Job Myth: GitRoll Introduces Programming Proficiency Scanner</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Finding the right engineer quickly is the key for all technology companies and startups. However, besides possessing excellent individual skills, whether a good engineer can effectively integrate into the team and collaborate with other engineers is also crucial.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GitRoll co-founder Cho Hsuan Yu (pictured in the top image) expressed that current enterprises often screen engineer talents based on external factors such as academic qualifications and relevant experiences during engineer recruitment. However, such practices may easily overlook engineers with less impressive diplomas. Additionally, relying solely on programming tests may not accurately reflect the candidate\'s ability to maintain programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recognizing the issues in the current recruitment systems, GitRoll combines the programming expertise of its team members with their backgrounds in enterprise promotion. They aim to develop a coding proficiency assessment system that can \'break down academic barriers\' and help compensate for the deficiencies of existing methods. \'We\'re like what \'Moneyball\' did in the movie; we speak through data rather than experience,\' said Feng Ruei Guo with a smile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The software engineer talent search engine launched by the GitRoll team categorizes individuals using data, much like \'Moneyball\', challenging the traditional notion that coding ability couldn\'t be quantified and assisting companies in finding suitable candidates.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Communication is Key: GitRoll Determines Engineer Value Through \'Five Forces\'</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you\'re using the GitRoll product, all HR needs to do is input the GitHub pages of their engineer candidates, and they can get an analysis of their coding ability within a few minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Security: Whether there are any cybersecurity or safety vulnerabilities.</li>\r\n	<li>Reliability: The number of errors (bugs) in the program.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintainability: How easy it is for others to understand and take over.</li>\r\n	<li>Influence: Reputation and status in the community.</li>\r\n	<li>Contribution: Performance and evaluation in collaborating on projects with other engineers online.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://image-cdn.learnin.tw/bnextmedia/image/album/2024-03/img-1711378814-14926.jpg?w=1200&amp;output=webp\" alt=\"GitRoll system diagram\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" style=\"width: 900px;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<p>GitRoll system offers a total of five analytical dimensions, encompassing an emphasis on the core programming skills of security, reliability, and maintainability, as well as the evaluation of engineers\' personal soft skills such as influence and community contribution. / Image Credits: GitRoll官網</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to being able to scan individual engineer profiles, the GitRoll system also provides a feature to store scan results. By uniformly comparing the analysis results of applicants with different abilities, it helps to find the candidates that best meet the expectations of the enterprise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although the GitRoll system currently only provides assessments of programming abilities and does not fully evaluate soft skills such as communication and collaboration, Feng Ruei Guo shared that the system has sparked enthusiastic discussions within the engineering community since its launch. Not only do engineers actively express their wishes for future functionalities, but also when the team is busy with enterprise development, engineers in the community voluntarily request public code for corrections. \'Because everyone wants to \'play\' with it, it\'s fair to say that the GitRoll system is being driven forward by the engineers themselves,\' said Feng Ruei Guo.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Becoming Alternative Global Talent Brokers: The Future Path of Startup GitRoll</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The GitRoll team, jokingly referring to themselves as \'alternative international human trafficker\', expressed their future plans to expand beyond building capability scanning systems and move towards the goal of \'engineer headhunting\'.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GitRoll will gradually expand its community influence by launching an engineer database. When companies want to recruit engineers, they can directly search on GitRoll\'s website and filter according to the types of engineers they are looking for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The team has completed the setting of the screening mechanism algorithm and has been in contact with engineers from different fields to expand the system database. Since its launch in November 2023, the GitRoll system has accumulated data from 5,000 engineers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite being established for less than half a year, the GitRoll team has learned from past entrepreneurial failures. They conducted market research after identifying market problems, confirming market size and product feasibility before delving into software development related to the field. Gradually, they have established a foothold in the relatively overlooked area of coding ability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With clear corporate goals and a team of aligned members, the next step for the GitRoll team is to venture into the larger U.S. market, which has greater industry demand. They aspire to explore and unearth underrated and buried engineering talents within the Asian community, aiming to build a bridge for them to enter the international market and assist them in pursuing a future where \'abilities speak\'.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>〔Original : Meet Global 〕\r\n	<br><a href=\"https://meet-global.bnext.com.tw/articles/view/48036\">https://meet-global.bnext.com.tw/articles/view/48036</a></p>', NULL, 1, '2024-04-29 06:56:26', '2024-04-29 07:00:37', NULL),
(633, 'SMESA Attended APEC SMEWG in Indonesia, Sharing Best Practice Cases of PPP Together with Taiwanese Enterprise', '2024-04-29', '', '<p>Deputy Director-General Wu Chia-ying of the Small and Medium Enterprise and Startup Administration (SMESA), Ministry of Economic Affairs led a delegation to attend the 57th APEC Small and Medium Enterprises Working Group Meeting held in Bali, Indonesia, from April 24th to 25th. Gogolook Co., Ltd. joined the meeting along with the delegation, and shared how the public-private partnership (PPP) mechanism has increased startup opportunities in the international market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the &nbsp;Government to Business Interaction &nbsp;session, Mr. Ian Huang, the Chief Financial Officer of Gogolook, shared the company s best practices, highlighting how startups can progress from the seed stage to the initial public offering with government funding support. Mr. Huang indicated that Gogolook provides digital solutions for anti-fraud. The company was grateful for receiving resources provided by the government, which formed the foundation for its early-stage business development. Through collaborative investments of National Development Fund and private funds, mentorship, and the assistance of corporate governance, startups can thrive and industries can innovate. Currently, Gogolook has partnered with law enforcement agencies in Korea, Japan, the Philippines, Thailand, and Malaysia to combat fraud internationally. On the achievement of public-private partnership, the Chair of the SMEWG, Mr. Aaron Sydor, responded that Taiwan s practice is innovative and constructive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The SMESA noted how Taiwan s outstanding digital technology can contribute to innovative product- and service-based tech startups. Additionally, SMESA highlighted government efforts to foster startup development by providing proving grounds, networks, and funding to support startup growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the APEC meeting, we additionally addressed the APEC economies on the ways SMESA has successfully integrated SMEs into global value chains. The APEC platform has increased domestic enterprise exposure to the international stage, which we expect to generate increased business opportunities abroad.</p>', NULL, 1, '2024-04-29 06:57:14', '2024-04-29 06:57:14', NULL),
(634, 'I See Taiwan, IC Grand Challenge', '2024-05-06', '', '<div dir=\"auto\">NSTC is hosting the \"IC Taiwan Grand Challenge\" to bolster Taiwan\'s IC startup ecosystem and attract global tech talent and investment.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Starting on May 14th at the Taiwan Chip-based Industrial Innovation Program (Taiwan CbI) launch event, it will explore how the semiconductor industry can capitalize on AI for innovation!&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">• Time: May. 14(Tue.) 10:00-12:00&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">• Venue: NTUH International Convention Center R201&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">▸▸SIGN UP NOW: <a href=\"https://user260169.pse.is/5t9zsc?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2XGd4id2TcN6v8toFtF-4qbguo9TwL8C_eL-z2aDIbPQXPImMrVX4mWRw_aem_Af7T7oMAnhKcaUY5Y5N6MsES604RchRFK4CBY5XsUNaxya0wXVD4lQW92jV-dOXXcacDMqyX46plRNV7F8kpePRI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://user260169.pse.is/5t9zsc</a></div>', NULL, 1, '2024-05-06 09:52:06', '2024-05-06 09:53:39', NULL),
(635, 'Garage+ 2024 must-see startups', '2024-05-13', '', '<p>In this era filled with challenges and opportunities, we are always in search of pioneers who dare to break boundaries and innovate. Just like the explorers of the Age of Discovery, entrepreneurs carry the mission of pioneering unknown territories, leading us towards a new future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Garage+ is partnering with Epoch to showcase cutting-edge innovations at the 2024 COMPUTEX exhibition from June 4th to 7th. Nearly 300 startups from 47 countries around the world will demonstrate unique technologies across various fields, from IoT &amp; Manufacturing, AI &amp; Data, to Energy &amp; Healthcare, and Digital Solutions, all of which are key directions for the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are looking to engage with entrepreneurs, seek collaboration opportunities, or obtain the latest industry information, we welcome you to visit the exhibition. Let us set sail together and create a better future!</p>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Date：June 4th, AM 9:30 to June 7th, PM 5:30 (GMT+8)</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Venue： Taipei Nangang Exhibition Center, Hall 2, 4th Floor, S0514 Section</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">More infomation：<a href=\"https://garageplus.asia/2024_mustsee/?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0ILm1KRxEHbbvknxJj9L9bwzo-DL1NMflnt9aSqgYkoYnxW0vRAovUCsU_aem_AYiabedu0TrndUoN4WwfF3SeXg8fR6bMtjhduYIU_c0JLGj-ZWUGUGolw7lkUKDYaqHPP45jWfVu0fEZIxCTru5x\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://garageplus.asia/2024_mustsee/</a></div>', NULL, 1, '2024-05-30 01:46:08', '2024-05-30 01:46:08', NULL),
(636, '2024 StarFab InnoVEX-Link the World, Lead to Growth!', '2024-05-17', '', '<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>・-・- 2024 StarFab InnoVEX -・-・</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Link the World, Lead to Growth!</strong></em></h4>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>StarFab at InnoVEX 2024 Series</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><em><strong>June 4 (Tuesday)</strong></em></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10:30-12:00 &nbsp;Asia New Bay Area Smart Technology Ecosystem - Constructing the Asia New Bay Area Innovation Ecosystem, Networking Event</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oganizer: Economic Development Bureau, Kaoshiung City Government\r\n	<br>Partners: iAMBITION TECHNOLOGY CO., LTD., InfinitiesSoft Solutions Inc., Syscom Computer&nbsp;Engineering Co Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>13:30-15:00 &nbsp;StarFab Pavilion Opening Ceremony</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Startups : iAmbition Technology、InfinitiesSoft Solutions Inc.、ioNetworks INC.、Profet AI、Spatial Topology Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><em><strong>&nbsp;June 5 (Wednesday)</strong></em></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10:00-12:00 &nbsp;CIAT Accelerator - Navigating the International Market with Generative AI: Enterprise and Startup AI Synergy for the Future</strong>\r\n	<br>Partners: Google Cloud Platform, NVIDIA, TWS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>13:30-15:30 &nbsp;AIoT Focused Accelerator - AI Innovations in Hsinchu County: Sustainable New Highlights</strong>\r\n	<br>Oganizer:&nbsp;Education Bureau of HsinChu County Government\r\n	<br>Partners: SYSTEX Corporation, MediaTek Inc., Moldintel, Leda Technology\r\n	<br>Startups : Profet AI、Spatial Topology Technology、Leda Technology、Moldintel、Asiabots Limited\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><em><strong>&nbsp;June 6 (Thursday)</strong></em></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>10:00-11:30 &nbsp;Flytech x StarFab Accelerator - Empowering Startups, Accelerating the Future</strong>\r\n	<br>Partners: Flytech technology co. ltd, Esltec, JENJAN\r\n	<br>Startups : Eslitec、JENJAN、BEARVFX、ChoozMo Inc</p>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n	<br>Date：June 4th, AM 9:30 to June 7th, PM 5:30 (GMT+8)</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Venue： Taipei Nangang Exhibition Center, Hall 2, 4th Floor, S0718 Section</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">More infomation：<a href=\"https://www.accupass.com/event/2405140919071988093503\">https://www.accupass.com/event/2405140919071988093503</a></div>', NULL, 1, '2024-05-30 01:52:02', '2024-05-30 01:52:02', NULL);
